Package: svHMM
Type: Package
Title: Fast Approximate Bayesian Inference for Stochastic Volatility Models Using Hidden Markov Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bruno E. Holtz <brunoeholtz@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Bruno E. Holtz <brunoeholtz@gmail.com>
Description: Implements fast approximate Bayesian inference methods for
    stochastic volatility in mean models with heavy-tailed distributions,
    using Hidden Markov Model approximations. The package relies on efficient
    C++ implementations via Rcpp, RcppParallel, and the GNU Scientific Library (GSL).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
SystemRequirements: GNU make, GSL (>= 2.1)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    RcppParallel (>= 5.0.0),
    RcppGSL,
    mvtnorm,
    invgamma
LinkingTo:
